66
00:03:11,310 --> 00:03:12,280
You're always eating.

67
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,560
Yingdan, have you noticed

68
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,400
Zhuge's been acting strange lately?

69
00:03:16,590 --> 00:03:17,520
Of course.

70
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,910
All clues about
assassinating Deng Yunfeng

71
00:03:19,910 --> 00:03:21,120
lead to the Sword Saint.

72
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,360
He had to return.

73
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:25,120
Crispy and delicious handmade pastries.

74
00:03:25,670 --> 00:03:26,510
Have a taste.

75
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,240
Sir, Miss,

76
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,190
look at these rabbits.

77
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:31,190
They're so cute, aren't they?

78
00:03:31,710 --> 00:03:32,910
Buy a pair and raise them.

79
00:03:32,910 --> 00:03:34,240
I promise, they'll

80
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,870
love each other

81
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:36,710
and have many children

82
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:37,590
just like you two.

83
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,590
What... Love each other?

84
00:03:40,430 --> 00:03:41,360
Stop saying nonsense!

85
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:42,960
Yingdan,

86
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:45,150
what does that mean?

87
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:46,840
Go away.

88
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:53,030
Yingdan.

89
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,560
If you like rabbits,

90
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:56,590
we can buy two and raise them.

91
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:58,310
Why would I buy them?

92
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,560
No.

93
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,630
I'm just looking.

94
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:04,150
Yingdan, do you think there's

95
00:04:04,150 --> 00:04:06,080
an animal immune to poison?

96
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:08,800
There's no such animal in this world.

97
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,710
I'm a small animal immune to poison.

98
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,200
Yingdan,

99
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:17,560
I will definitely find

100
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,590
an animal immune to poison

101
00:04:18,590 --> 00:04:19,430
and give it to you.

102
00:04:24,420 --> 00:04:27,300
(Righteousness)

103
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:30,000
Heng, you've gone too far.

104
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,270
You've been away for half a year

105
00:04:31,270 --> 00:04:32,110
and never returned.

106
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,010
Uncle.

107
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:37,430
Can you untie this for me?

108
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:43,560
Why would you tie such a tight knot?

109
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,000
I...

110
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,190
Where was I just now?

111
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:50,270
Been away for half a year.

112
00:04:50,270 --> 00:04:51,110
Yes.

113
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,630
You've been away for half a year.

114
00:04:52,630 --> 00:04:54,480
If your dad died,
wouldn't you come back?

115
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,320
- That old man...
- I...

116
00:04:55,750 --> 00:04:57,270
He pretends to be dead all the time.

117
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,360
Am I supposed to rush home every time?

118
00:04:59,750 --> 00:05:00,640
That's right.

119
00:05:00,650 --> 00:05:01,510
Over the years,

120
00:05:01,510 --> 00:05:03,270
he's faked his death many times.

121
00:05:03,630 --> 00:05:05,270
But it's because he misses you, right?

122
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:06,430
Okay, enough.

123
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:09,310
I came back this time to ask you

124
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,920
who else in the Sword Alliance
can use the Shadow Swordplay

125
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,510
other than my dad?

126
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:19,160
It's our ultimate skill.

127
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,750
Over the years,
only your dad can master it.

128
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,120
What is

129
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,630
this old man thinking?

130
00:05:29,190 --> 00:05:30,870
He's neglecting his duties.

131
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,560
We should thrive through martial arts.

132
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,950
How can we get tainted
by greed and wealth?

133
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,310
I've been telling him this,

134
00:05:37,310 --> 00:05:38,190
but he never listens.

135
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,310
Where is he right now?

136
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:44,310
He didn't know you'd come back

137
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,390
for his fake death.

138
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:48,720
So, after leaving that message,

139
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,040
he went to Huizhou to find you.

140
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,000
Went to Huizhou?

141
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,320
It's good.

142
00:05:58,870 --> 00:05:59,870
It's inconvenient

143
00:06:00,190 --> 00:06:01,480
to do it here.

144
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:03,840
You...

145
00:06:04,270 --> 00:06:05,160
What did you say?

146
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:07,790
Oh, nothing.

147
00:06:08,950 --> 00:06:09,830
I'll take my leave.

148
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,360
No time to waste. Goodbye, Uncle.

149
00:06:11,630 --> 00:06:13,560
Heng, Heng! Wait a minute!

150
00:06:13,780 --> 00:06:15,430
(Sword Alliance)
Master! Master!

151
00:06:15,430 --> 00:06:16,310
Let's go!

152
00:06:16,310 --> 00:06:17,150
Heng.

153
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,480
Who are they?

154
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:21,390
Uncle, they are my friends.

155
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,430
This is Gou Lingfeng.

156
00:06:22,430 --> 00:06:23,270
This is Ma Yingdan.

157
00:06:23,630 --> 00:06:24,470
This is my second uncle,

158
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:26,430
Zhuge Xun, the vice leader
of Sword Alliance.

159
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:27,870
Hello, Vice Leader.

160
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:28,840
Hello, Vice Leader.

161
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:30,670
Heng,

162
00:06:30,830 --> 00:06:31,680
come home.

163
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,240
After all, this is your home.

164
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:34,640
I have no home.

165
00:06:35,770 --> 00:06:37,270
- Watch your words.
- Vice Leader,

166
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:39,000
I've noticed that

167
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:41,120
the layout of the shops and streets
is similar to

168
00:06:41,270 --> 00:06:42,830
the Gou Family Trade Association.

169
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:43,750
Are you

170
00:06:43,750 --> 00:06:45,190
imitating us?

171
00:06:45,190 --> 00:06:46,030
Nonsense.

172
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,920
Our streets

173
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,920
were all designed by your father.

174
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:53,310
My father?

175
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,800
- It's really your family's work.
- Yes.

176
00:06:58,070 --> 00:06:58,910
Heng,

177
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,560
do you have to leave in such a hurry?

178
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:02,120
I asked Auntie Wang to make

179
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,430
your favorite braised pork.

180
00:07:03,430 --> 00:07:04,720
Uncle, we'll skip the meal.

181
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,600
I'm really in a hurry.

182
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:06,830
Goodbye, Uncle.

183
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:07,670
Let's go.

184
00:07:14,270 --> 00:07:15,430
Go, go!

185
00:07:16,390 --> 00:07:17,560
Go, go!

186
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:27,470
Zhuge.

187
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,480
You're rushing to find your father.

188
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,750
Do you think
he assassinated Deng Yunfeng?

189
00:07:35,190 --> 00:07:36,310
How's that possible?

190
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,360
He's the noble Sword Saint.

191
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,390
Assassinating Deng Yunfeng

192
00:07:39,390 --> 00:07:41,000
would stain his hands.

193
00:07:44,830 --> 00:07:45,670
Master.

194
00:07:46,870 --> 00:07:48,070
I need your help.

195
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,160
Stop resisting!

196
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:10,750
You're going to die today!

197
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:11,920
No way!

198
00:08:12,430 --> 00:08:13,480
I, Zhuge Heng,

199
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:15,560
haven't fulfilled my three aspirations.

200
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:20,480
Don't drink the Oblivion Soup

201
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:22,920
and save your dreams for your next life.

202
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,510
Demonic remnant,

203
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:31,870
