204
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:33,440
Senior,

205
00:08:33,800 --> 00:08:35,720
sorry for this.

206
00:08:38,870 --> 00:08:40,160
You're really in Huizhou.

207
00:08:40,830 --> 00:08:43,200
Zhuge, calm down.

208
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:45,270
We haven't asked him
about the assassination.

209
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:47,200
It's hard to lure you out.

210
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,600
- Heng...
- Don't call me Heng!

211
00:08:50,390 --> 00:08:51,870
Today, I'm going to kill you

212
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,750
to avenge my mother!

213
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:56,030
Zhuge! Zhuge!

214
00:08:56,030 --> 00:08:58,240
Get off me!

215
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,080
Senior,

216
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,200
is there some

217
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,200
misunderstanding?

218
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,270
What misunderstanding?

219
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,390
He's nothing but a vain

220
00:09:04,390 --> 00:09:05,910
and selfish hypocrite!

221
00:09:05,910 --> 00:09:06,750
Heng.

222
00:09:07,270 --> 00:09:09,320
What happened back then
isn't what you think.

223
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:11,150
Get off me.

224
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,200
Zhuge...

225
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,280
Zhuge Yu.

226
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,360
You're a scum!

227
00:09:18,510 --> 00:09:19,870
The biggest mistake my mom made

228
00:09:19,870 --> 00:09:20,790
was to marry you.

229
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:22,960
You don't deserve to be my father.

230
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,080
I truly wish

231
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,600
I was someone else's son.

232
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,560
Unfilial son!

233
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:36,870
Don't you dare insult
your mother's spirit.

234
00:09:46,670 --> 00:09:47,670
I was right.

235
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,480
You're so angry.

236
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:55,080
It turns out I'm really not your son.

237
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,240
You...

238
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,080
Senior.

239
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,440
Hit me.

240
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,840
Come on, hit me.

241
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,720
Why don't you kill me?

242
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,630
- Heng!
- Don't call me Heng!

243
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:22,960
Zhuge.

244
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:31,910
I, Zhuge Heng,

245
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:33,800
swear

246
00:10:35,630 --> 00:10:36,870
on my blood

247
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,360
and my sword

248
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:44,600
to challenge Zhuge Yu, the Sword Saint,

249
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:49,120
to a Sword Oath Duel!

250
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:54,870
You want to challenge me to a duel?

251
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:58,480
Do you know what it means?

252
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:04,320
Hasn't the title of Sword Saint always been

253
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:06,000
the most important thing to you?

254
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:11,510
I will take it from you.

255
00:11:15,670 --> 00:11:16,600
Okay.

256
00:11:20,750 --> 00:11:22,080
Tomorrow at noon,

257
00:11:22,670 --> 00:11:24,120
let's fight at the drill ground!

258
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,030
Okay!

259
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:34,870
Senior,

260
00:11:34,870 --> 00:11:35,790
please wait.

261
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:39,030
I have a small question.

262
00:11:41,510 --> 00:11:42,670
Who are you?

263
00:11:43,670 --> 00:11:45,030
I am Gou Lingfeng.

264
00:11:45,270 --> 00:11:47,960
Chairman Gou of the Gou Family
Trade Association is my father.

265
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,910
Gou's son?

266
00:11:53,510 --> 00:11:55,270
Why did you learn demonic skills?

267
00:11:56,390 --> 00:11:58,270
That's a long story.

268
00:11:58,510 --> 00:11:59,790
All you need to know is

269
00:11:59,790 --> 00:12:01,390
I have a kind heart.

270
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:04,440
Fine.

271
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:05,960
What's the matter?

272
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:10,270
As for the assassination of Deng Yunfeng
from the Martial Artists Association,

273
00:12:10,270 --> 00:12:11,110
you...

274
00:12:13,150 --> 00:12:15,000
I've heard about it.

275
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:17,320
Are you asking me if I did this?

276
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,510
Listen,

277
00:12:19,670 --> 00:12:20,870
if I were the one,

278
00:12:21,150 --> 00:12:23,030
Deng Yunfeng wouldn't have
withstood five moves.

279
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,510
He really didn't withstand five moves.

280
00:12:25,510 --> 00:12:26,600
You did it.

281
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:29,550
I mean, he would've died
within five moves!

