00:12:33,870 --> 00:12:34,710
Senior,

283
00:12:35,670 --> 00:12:38,240
Zhuge and you...

284
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:41,630
This is a family affair.

285
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:45,270
Since you're his friend,

286
00:12:45,670 --> 00:12:47,030
please look after him for me.

287
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:50,200
Don't let him do anything reckless.

288
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:08,320
Zhuge.

289
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,080
Heng,

290
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,160
I'll drink with you.

291
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,790
Ling'er, you...

292
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,040
Gou Lingfeng,

293
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:25,120
what's going on here?

294
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:31,150
The enemy Zhuge often mentions

295
00:13:31,550 --> 00:13:33,030
turns out to be his father.

296
00:13:35,550 --> 00:13:36,790
And he challenged his father

297
00:13:36,790 --> 00:13:39,000
to a Sword Oath Duel.

298
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:40,910
Sword Oath Duel?

299
00:13:43,150 --> 00:13:43,990
Oh, no.

300
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:46,960
The Sword Oath Duel

301
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:49,750
is a deathmatch to decide
the Sword Alliance's Sword Saint.

302
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,480
Once the current Sword Saint

303
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,520
accepts the challenge,

304
00:13:52,520 --> 00:13:53,870
there's no holding back.

305
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,390
The winner

306
00:13:57,390 --> 00:13:58,750
will be the next Sword Saint.

307
00:13:59,390 --> 00:14:00,230
Zhuge,

308
00:14:00,630 --> 00:14:02,910
do you really hate your dad that much?

309
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:04,790
Is there some misunderstanding?

310
00:14:04,790 --> 00:14:06,270
You don't know what I've been through.

311
00:14:07,750 --> 00:14:08,960
You won't understand.

312
00:14:12,750 --> 00:14:14,960
I must reveal
that hypocrite's true colors.

313
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:17,480
- But he's your father!
- Yes.

314
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:19,320
How could you wield your sword
to attack him?

315
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:21,080
I've made up my mind.
Don't try to stop me.

316
00:14:24,100 --> 00:14:25,130
Heng,

317
00:14:25,270 --> 00:14:27,080
every parent loves their children,

318
00:14:27,670 --> 00:14:29,550
including the Sword Saint.

319
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:30,910
If misunderstandings

320
00:14:30,910 --> 00:14:32,440
lead to disaster,

321
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:34,000
you'll regret it
for the rest of your life.

322
00:14:37,790 --> 00:14:39,440
For the title of Sword Saint,

323
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,750
he killed my mother.

324
00:14:44,860 --> 00:14:46,900
(Righteousness)

325
00:14:46,910 --> 00:14:48,030
Are you really

326
00:14:48,750 --> 00:14:49,960
a member of the demonic sect?

327
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:51,480
What if I am?

328
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:53,840
What if I'm not?

329
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:55,480
I'm asking you again.

330
00:14:56,630 --> 00:14:58,150
Are you really a demonic sect member?

331
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,080
Yes.

332
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:02,200
I'm the Demonic Witch

333
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:04,240
that everyone wants to kill.

334
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,080
Do you want to kill me?

335
00:15:08,390 --> 00:15:09,320
Demonic Witch!

336
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,360
Kill her!

337
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:12,120
Zhuge Yu,
you're the Demonic Witch's ally!

338
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,480
You don't deserve to be our leader!

339
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:16,080
Kill her, kill her, kill her!

340
00:15:22,670 --> 00:15:24,510
I saw him kill my mother
with my own eyes,

341
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:27,480
so I must kill him

342
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:29,200
to avenge my mother!

343
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:34,790
I see.

344
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:37,960
Your mother was a member
of the demonic sect,

345
00:15:39,030 --> 00:15:40,320
so you've longed to

346
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,510
join the demonic sect

347
00:15:41,670 --> 00:15:43,080
and learn that demonic skill

348
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:44,200
to avenge your mother.

349
00:15:44,390 --> 00:15:45,910
I saw their duel before.

350
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:47,630
Whenever my mother used

351
00:15:47,630 --> 00:15:49,000
the Moon Sword Skill,

352
00:15:49,510 --> 00:15:51,080
she could defeat Zhuge Yu.

353
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:54,270
So, I must learn that move.

354
00:16:27,030 --> 00:16:30,080
Is the Sword Saint allergic to the moon?

355
00:16:30,870 --> 00:16:31,710
What did you say?

356
00:16:32,150 --> 00:16:33,270
Ridiculous.

357
00:16:42,670 --> 00:16:43,550
That's all?

358
00:16:46,790 --> 00:16:47,630
Zhuge,

359
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:50,120
you should confirm it.

360
00:16:50,390 --> 00:16:51,510
Can your father

361
00:16:51,510 --> 00:16:54,120
really be defeated by that sword skill?

362
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,160
Exactly.

363
00:16:55,630 --> 00:16:57,150
You can't even defeat me with that move.

364
00:16:57,150 --> 00:16:59,270
I wonder who bewitched him.

365
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:04,080
What's wrong with Ling'er?

366
00:17:04,390 --> 00:17:06,390
It's not that weak, right?

367
00:17:10,030 --> 00:17:10,960
Ms. Ling'er...

368
00:17:12,870 --> 00:17:14,000
How dare you slap me?

369
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:16,030
Why did you teach Zhuge Heng
that sword skill?

370
00:17:16,030 --> 00:17:17,440
Do you want to harm him?

371
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:18,510
Harm him?

372
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:20,350
Do you know Zhuge Heng's biggest wish

373
00:17:20,350 --> 00:17:21,440
is to learn that sword skill

374
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:22,550
and get revenge?

375
00:17:22,550 --> 00:17:23,720
Do you think you can help him?

376
00:17:23,720 --> 00:17:24,960
Do you know who his enemy

377
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:25,880
is?

378
00:17:26,310 --> 00:17:27,830
Do you know he wants to kill

379
00:17:27,830 --> 00:17:29,030
his father?

380
00:17:30,350 --> 00:17:31,240
What?

381
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:36,640
I'm Zhuge Yu, the 7th Sword Saint
of the Sword Alliance.

382
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:39,790
Today, I accept Zhuge Heng's
Sword Oath Duel challenge.

383
00:17:41,510 --> 00:17:42,880
I swear on my blood

384
00:17:44,270 --> 00:17:45,480
and my sword,

385
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:47,030
if you defeat me,

386
00:17:47,310 --> 00:17:49,000
you'll be the 8th Sword Saint.

387
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:50,510
What Sword Saint?

388
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:52,350
It means nothing to me.

389
00:17:53,350 --> 00:17:54,640
I only want to kill you.

390
00:17:55,270 --> 00:17:57,440
- Sword Saint is Zhuge's father.
- So what?

391
00:17:57,440 --> 00:17:59,200
I am Zhuge's master.

392
00:17:59,750 --> 00:18:00,720
So, should I call

393
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,830
the Sword Saint brother?

394
00:18:03,720 --> 00:18:04,560
Shut up.

395
00:18:05,200 --> 00:18:06,160
It's not something

396
00:18:06,310 --> 00:18:07,640
that outsiders can gossip about.

397
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:08,720
Come, Heng.

398
00:18:09,030 --> 00:18:10,480
Show me what you've got.

399
00:18:10,480 --> 00:18:12,830
Have your sword techniques improved?

400
00:18:19,030 --> 00:18:20,070
Your strike is too slow,

401
00:18:20,070 --> 00:18:21,030
and the angle is wrong.

402
00:18:27,350 --> 00:18:28,310
Heng,

403
00:18:28,310 --> 00:18:30,000
your martial arts are unfocused,

404
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:31,510
and your True Qi is a mess.

405
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:34,750
It seems you've been blinded by hatred.

406
00:18:34,750 --> 00:18:36,070
You've been too impatient

407
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,640
and wasted your talent.

408
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:39,030
Don't try to teach me!

409
00:19:34,640 --> 00:19:36,400
Mom, you're pretty and powerful.

410
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:37,550
Dad, you're so silly.

411
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:42,030
Heng, you're right.

412
00:19:42,030 --> 00:19:43,000
I'm so silly.

413
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:44,680
I still can't counter that move.

414
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:46,110
Mom,

415
00:19:46,110 --> 00:19:47,400
what's this move?

416
00:19:47,400 --> 00:19:48,790
I want to learn it.

417
00:19:49,070 --> 00:19:50,790
If my dad bullies me,

418
00:19:50,790 --> 00:19:52,790
I'll use it to teach him a lesson.

419
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:53,960
When you grow up,

420
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:55,310
I'll teach you this move.

421
00:19:55,510 --> 00:19:56,720
If your dad dares to bully you,

422
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:58,000
you'll use it to defeat him.

423
00:19:58,180 --> 00:19:59,030
That's right.

424
00:19:59,030 --> 00:20:00,400
If you learn this move,

425
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:02,030
I won't dare to bully you anymore.

426
00:20:02,030 --> 00:20:03,400
Do you want to bully Heng?

427
00:20:07,920 --> 00:20:08,760
I wouldn't dare.

428
00:20:20,510 --> 00:20:21,350
Heng!

429
00:20:21,730 --> 00:20:22,580
Zhuge.

430
00:20:22,590 --> 00:20:24,110
- How did you learn this?
- Heng!

431
00:20:24,750 --> 00:20:25,920
Who taught you?

432
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:27,720
The Sword Oath Duel

433
00:20:28,270 --> 00:20:29,750
cannot be interfered with by others.

434
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:31,590
- Zhuge.
- Only this move

435
00:20:31,590 --> 00:20:32,880
can defeat you.

436
00:20:35,350 --> 00:20:37,350
I can't believe you did this to me.

437
00:20:37,720 --> 00:20:39,640
Didn't you do the same to my mother?

438
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:42,510
I didn't kill your mother!

439
00:20:42,830 --> 00:20:44,240
I saw it with my own eyes!

440
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,270
I wanted to save her!

441
00:20:46,510 --> 00:20:47,350
Save her?

442
00:20:47,790 --> 00:20:48,920
Did you save her

443
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:51,160
by stabbing her with a sword?

444
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:53,110
I didn't!

445
00:20:53,960 --> 00:20:54,960
Enough.

446
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:56,590
Prepare to die!

447
00:20:56,830 --> 00:20:58,070
Zhuge! Zhuge!

448
00:20:58,070 --> 00:20:59,270
- Zhuge!
- Heng!

449
00:21:03,310 --> 00:21:04,150
Zhuge.

450
00:21:05,310 --> 00:21:06,310
I hereby declare

451
00:21:06,310 --> 00:21:08,720
the winner of the 7th Sword Oath Duel

452
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:09,680
is Zhuge Heng.

453
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:14,000
Senior!

454
00:21:23,110 --> 00:21:24,110
Sword Saint!

455
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:25,840
Senior.

456
00:21:31,510 --> 00:21:32,350
Senior.

457
00:21:32,590 --> 00:21:33,680
You're seriously injured.

458
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:34,790
You still need

459
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:36,920
to rest for a few months.

460
00:21:37,750 --> 00:21:38,590
Senior,

461
00:21:38,750 --> 00:21:41,440
what happened between you and Zhuge?

462
00:21:43,790 --> 00:21:44,920
It's all in the past.

463
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:46,480
I don't want to bring it up.

464
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:47,680
Besides...

465
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:48,680
You...

466
00:21:48,840 --> 00:21:50,200
- Well...
- Even if Heng knows,

467
00:21:50,200 --> 00:21:51,680
it won't change anything.

468
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:53,510
He'll only be heartbroken.

469
00:21:53,510 --> 00:21:55,350
Senior, do you really want to be his enemy

470
00:21:55,350 --> 00:21:56,790
for the rest of your life?

471
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:57,920
Senior,

472
00:21:57,920 --> 00:21:59,960
since I met Zhuge Heng,

473
00:22:00,550 --> 00:22:01,720
he's been trying to

474
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:03,310
join the demonic sect

475
00:22:03,310 --> 00:22:05,720
to learn that sword skill to defeat you.

476
00:22:06,510 --> 00:22:08,830
He's been living in pain.

477
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:10,310
Do you really want him

478
00:22:10,830 --> 00:22:12,440
to get lost

479
00:22:12,440 --> 00:22:13,750
go astray?

480
00:22:17,270 --> 00:22:19,200
Does he know his mother
was a demonic sect member?

481
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:21,920
It's not a secret.

482
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:23,110
He knew it all along.

483
00:22:23,110 --> 00:22:25,640
Why else would he want
to join the demonic sect?

484
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:30,240
- Senior!
- Senior!

485
00:22:33,590 --> 00:22:34,590
Does it still hurt?

486
00:22:35,110 --> 00:22:35,950
No.

487
00:22:38,270 --> 00:22:39,510
You totally deserved it!

488
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:45,110
I'm sorry, Ling'er.

489
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:46,640
You must be worried.

490
00:22:48,790 --> 00:22:49,680
A while ago,

491
00:22:53,270 --> 00:22:55,550
you went to Linglong's place
to train every night.

492
00:22:55,960 --> 00:22:57,110
I saw it.

493
00:22:57,110 --> 00:22:58,790
I was eager to practice sword skills.

494
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:00,000
Don't get me wrong.

495
00:23:02,830 --> 00:23:04,200
I believe you.

496
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:06,830
Since I learned about your burden,

497
00:23:07,110 --> 00:23:08,590
I've believed you.

498
00:23:09,960 --> 00:23:11,550
Sword Saint should be awake.

499
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:12,790
Talk to him

500
00:23:12,790 --> 00:23:14,270
and make things clear.

501
00:23:14,510 --> 00:23:15,350
I'm not going.

502
00:23:15,590 --> 00:23:16,830
Will you go or not?

503
00:23:16,830 --> 00:23:18,000
Fine, I'll go!

504
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:19,550
I'll go, okay?

505
00:23:34,070 --> 00:23:35,480
I thought I could

506
00:23:36,440 --> 00:23:38,750
help Shun keep this secret.

507
00:23:40,590 --> 00:23:42,550
But Heng found out.

508
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:46,310
I'm so stupid.

509
00:23:47,790 --> 00:23:50,200
He's been holding a grudge
against me all these years.

510
00:23:55,270 --> 00:23:56,540
(Righteousness)
Zhuge Yu,

511
00:23:56,550 --> 00:23:58,400
as the leader of the Sword Alliance,

512
00:23:58,400 --> 00:24:00,270
how could you marry this Demonic Witch?

513
00:24:00,640 --> 00:24:03,030
You're a disgrace
to the righteous martial sects!

514
00:24:03,030 --> 00:24:03,870
Indeed!

515
00:24:04,110 --> 00:24:05,680
As members of
the Martial Artists Association,

516
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:06,960
we should stand united as one.

517
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:08,440
However, you've ruined the

518
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:10,030
century-long prestige
of the Sword Alliance!

519
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:11,510
Zhuge Yu,

520
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:13,270
you're a disgrace to the martial world!

521
00:24:22,160 --> 00:24:23,200
Are you really

522
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:25,000
a demonic sect member?

523
00:24:25,830 --> 00:24:26,880
What if I am?

524
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:29,240
What if I'm not?

525
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:31,920
Let me ask you again.

526
00:24:32,790 --> 00:24:34,400
Are you really a demonic sect member?

527
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:37,320
Yes.

528
00:24:37,510 --> 00:24:38,400
I'm the Demonic Witch

529
00:24:38,400 --> 00:24:40,480
that everyone wants to kill.

530
00:24:42,030 --> 00:24:43,200
Are you going to kill me?

531
00:24:46,070 --> 00:24:47,030
No...

532
00:24:47,030 --> 00:24:48,030
Demonic Witch!

533
00:24:48,030 --> 00:24:49,000
Kill her!

534
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:51,550
Zhuge Yu, you're
the Demonic Witch's ally.

535
00:24:51,550 --> 00:24:52,880
You don't deserve to be our leader!

536
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:54,480
- Kill her!
- Kill her! Kill her!

537
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:55,590
Kill me!

538
00:24:55,880 --> 00:24:56,880
Shun!

539
00:24:57,070 --> 00:24:58,030
Kill me,

540
00:24:58,550 --> 00:25:00,440
and you'll secure
the title of the Sword Saint,

541
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:02,400
protect the reputation
of the Sword Alliance,

542
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:03,480
and erase

543
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:05,830
the shame I've brought upon you.

544
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:12,850
You've never brought me shame.

545
00:25:12,850 --> 00:25:13,760
We...

546
00:25:17,830 --> 00:25:18,670
Shun!

547
00:25:21,510 --> 00:25:22,480
Heng...

548
00:25:23,310 --> 00:25:24,640
Take care of Heng...

549
00:25:33,510 --> 00:25:35,440
Don't let him know

550
00:25:37,750 --> 00:25:38,680
his mother...

551
00:25:43,310 --> 00:25:45,000
was a demonic sect member.

552
00:25:49,480 --> 00:25:50,320
Okay...

553
00:25:57,790 --> 00:26:00,110
To protect me and Heng,

554
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:03,030
Shun threw herself onto the sword.

555
00:26:06,070 --> 00:26:07,720
I couldn't pull back in time.

556
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:11,880
It was all my fault!

557
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:23,510
The day I met Shun,

558
00:26:24,790 --> 00:26:27,000
I already knew her identity.

559
00:26:28,270 --> 00:26:29,400
I didn't care

560
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:31,110
whether she was
from the demonic sect or not.

561
00:26:31,480 --> 00:26:32,400
All I knew was

562
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:33,680
that she was kind

563
00:26:34,030 --> 00:26:35,440
and brave.

564
00:26:35,830 --> 00:26:37,680
She was the one and only

565
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:39,200
in my life!

566
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:44,110
However,

567
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:48,640
I never told her any of this.

568
00:26:51,510 --> 00:26:53,200
